data.title: Oak Hill WV: The Death of Hank Williams Sr. Part 1
data.meta_description: Located in "downtown" Oak Hill, this sign was actually erected by the Alabama Tourism Commission. West Virginia has had a sign along US 119 south of Oak Hill for many years. The concerts he was forced to skip noted on the sign, were scheduled for the Charleston Municipal Auditorium (flic.kr/p/e4n7iq).
